HEADWORD: Bramah press
<hw>Bra"mah press`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A hydrostatic press of
immense power, invented by Joseph <xex>Bramah</xex> of London. See under
<er>Hydrostatic</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bramble</ent>⟦br⟧
